<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>flowbrain — install guide</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;600&display=swap');
  *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
  body{font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;background:#0f0f13;color:#e8e6f0;padding:24px 20px 48px;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto}
  h1{font-size:28px;font-weight:600;color:#e8e6f0;margin-bottom:4px}
  h1 span{color:#a78bfa}
  .subtitle{font-size:14px;color:#555;margin-bottom:32px}
  .phase{margin-bottom:36px}
  .phase-title{font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:#a78bfa;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:14px}
  .step{background:#16161f;border:1px solid #222230;border-radius:16px;padding:16px;margin-bottom:10px;display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:flex-start}
  .step-num{width:28px;height:28px;background:#a78bfa22;border:1px solid #a78bfa44;border-radius:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#a78bfa;flex-shrink:0;font-family:monospace}
  .step-body{}
  .step-title{font-size:14px;font-weight:500;color:#e8e6f0;margin-bottom:4px}
  .step-desc{font-size:13px;color:#888;line-height:1.5}
  .step-desc a{color:#a78bfa;text-decoration:none}
  .step-desc code{background:#1a1a28;border:1px solid #2a2a3a;border-radius:6px;padding:2px 7px;font-size:12px;color:#c4b5fd;font-family:monospace}
  .tip{background:#1a3d38;border:1px solid #1a5d48;border-radius:12px;padding:12px 14px;margin-top:10px;font-size:13px;color:#4ade80;line-height:1.5}
  .tip strong{color:#86efac}
  .warn{background:#3d2e10;border:1px solid #5d4010;border-radius:12px;padding:12px 14px;margin-top:10px;font-size:13px;color:#fbbf24;line-height:1.5}
  .files-list{background:#16161f;border:1px solid #222230;border-radius:16px;padding:16px;margin-bottom:10px}
  .file-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #1a1a24;font-size:13px}
  .file-row:last-child{border-bottom:none}
  .file-icon{font-size:16px;flex-shrink:0}
  .file-name{font-family:monospace;color:#c4b5fd;font-size:12px}
  .file-desc{color:#555;font-size:12px;margin-left:auto}
  .hero{background:#1a1528;border:1px solid #a78bfa33;border-radius:20px;padding:24px;margin-bottom:32px;text-align:center}
  .hero-emoji{font-size:48px;margin-bottom:12px}
  .hero-text{font-size:15px;color:#888;line-height:1.6}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>flow<span>brain</span> install guide</h1>
<p class="subtitle">How to get your app onto your phone — step by step, no experience needed</p>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-emoji">📱</div>
  <div class="hero-text">By the end of this guide, flowbrain will be installed on your phone's home screen like a real app — with its own icon, full-screen view, and offline support.</div>
</div>

<div class="phase">
  <div class="phase-title">phase 1 — create a free GitHub account</div>
  <div class="step"><div class="step-num">1</div><div class="step-body"><div class="step-title">Go to github.com</div><div class="step-desc">Open <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank">github.com</a> on your computer and click <strong>Sign up</strong>. It's completely free — no credit card needed.</div></div></div>
  <div class="step"><div class="step-num">2</div><div class="step-body"><div class="step-title">Create your account</div><div class="step-desc">Enter your email, create a password, and choose a username. Verify your email when prompted.</div></div></div>
</div>

<div class="phase">
  <div class="phase-title">phase 2 — create a new repository</div>
  <div class="step"><div class="step-num">3</div><div class="step-body"><div class="step-title">Click the + button → New repository</div><div class="step-desc">Once logged in, click the <strong>+</strong> icon in the top-right corner and select <strong>New repository</strong>.</div></div></div>
  <div class="step"><div class="step-num">4</div><div class="step-body"><div class="step-title">Name it <code>flowbrain</code></div><div class="step-desc">Set the name to <code>flowbrain</code>, make sure it's set to <strong>Public</strong>, tick <strong>Add a README file</strong>, then click <strong>Create repository</strong>.</div></div></div>
</div>

<div class="phase">
  <div class="phase-title">phase 3 — upload your files</div>
  <div class="step"><div class="step-num">5</div><div class="step-body"><div class="step-title">Click "uploading an existing file"</div><div class="step-desc">On your new repository page you'll see a link that says <em>"uploading an existing file"</em> — click it.</div></div></div>
  <div class="step"><div class="step-num">6</div><div class="step-body">
    <div class="step-title">Upload all these files</div>
    <div class="step-desc">Drag and drop all the files from the zip you downloaded into the upload area. Make sure the <code>icons</code> folder is included.</div>
    <div class="files-list" style="margin-top:10px">
      <div class="file-row"><span class="file-icon">📄</span><span class="file-name">index.html</span><span class="file-desc">main app</span></div>
      <div class="file-row"><span class="file-icon">🎨</span><span class="file-name">style.css</span><span class="file-desc">all styling</span></div>
      <div class="file-row"><span class="file-icon">⚙️</span><span class="file-name">app.js</span><span class="file-desc">app logic</span></div>
      <div class="file-row"><span class="file-icon">📋</span><span class="file-name">manifest.json</span><span class="file-desc">PWA config</span></div>
      <div class="file-row"><span class="file-icon">🔧</span><span class="file-name">sw.js</span><span class="file-desc">offline support</span></div>
      <div class="file-row"><span class="file-icon">📁</span><span class="file-name">icons/icon-192.png</span><span class="file-desc">app icon</span></div>
      <div class="file-row"><span class="file-icon">📁</span><span class="file-name">icons/icon-512.png</span><span class="file-desc">app icon (large)</span></div>
    </div>
  </div></div></div>
  <div class="step"><div class="step-num">7</div><div class="step-body"><div class="step-title">Commit the files</div><div class="step-desc">Scroll down, leave the commit message as-is, and click <strong>Commit changes</strong>. Your files are now uploaded.</div></div></div>
</div>

<div class="phase">
  <div class="phase-title">phase 4 — turn on GitHub Pages (free hosting)</div>
  <div class="step"><div class="step-num">8</div><div class="step-body"><div class="step-title">Go to Settings → Pages</div><div class="step-desc">In your repository, click the <strong>Settings</strong> tab at the top, then scroll down and click <strong>Pages</strong> in the left sidebar.</div></div></div>
  <div class="step"><div class="step-num">9</div><div class="step-body"><div class="step-title">Set the source to "main" branch</div><div class="step-desc">Under <strong>Source</strong>, select <strong>Deploy from a branch</strong>, choose <strong>main</strong> as the branch, leave folder as <strong>/ (root)</strong>, and click <strong>Save</strong>.</div></div></div>
  <div class="step"><div class="step-num">10</div><div class="step-body"><div class="step-title">Wait 2 minutes, then visit your URL</div><div class="step-desc">GitHub will give you a URL like: <code>https://yourusername.github.io/flowbrain</code> — this is your live app! Visit it on your phone.</div></div></div>
  <div class="tip"><strong>Tip:</strong> It can take up to 5 minutes for GitHub Pages to go live the first time. If you see a 404, just wait a minute and refresh.</div>
</div>

<div class="phase">
  <div class="phase-title">phase 5 — install on your phone</div>
  <div class="step"><div class="step-num">11</div><div class="step-body"><div class="step-title">On iPhone (Safari)</div><div class="step-desc">Open the URL in <strong>Safari</strong> (not Chrome). Tap the <strong>Share button</strong> (the box with an arrow), scroll down, and tap <strong>Add to Home Screen</strong>. Tap <strong>Add</strong>.</div></div></div>
  <div class="step"><div class="step-num">12</div><div class="step-body"><div class="step-title">On Android (Chrome)</div><div class="step-desc">Open the URL in <strong>Chrome</strong>. Tap the <strong>three dots</strong> menu in the top right, then tap <strong>Add to Home screen</strong>. Tap <strong>Add</strong>.</div></div></div>
  <div class="tip"><strong>You're done!</strong> flowbrain now appears on your home screen like a real app. Open it — it runs full-screen with no browser bar, works offline, and remembers all your data.</div>
</div>

<div class="phase">
  <div class="phase-title">need help?</div>
  <div class="step"><div class="step-num">💬</div><div class="step-body"><div class="step-title">Ask Claude!</div><div class="step-desc">If you get stuck at any step, just describe what you see to Claude and it'll walk you through it. You can also ask Claude to update the app with new features any time — just share the files and ask.</div></div></div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
